%% Diagram: Request Coalescing in Discord Data Services
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Users A,B,C
    participant DS as Data Service
    participant DB as ScyllaDB

    U->>DS: 3 GETs\nchannel=42 (hash → same DS)
    Note over DS: First req spawns worker.\nB and C subscribe to it.
    DS->>DB: SELECT messages\n(channel_id=42, bucket=N)
    DB-->>DS: rows
    DS-->>U: fan-out same result\nto all 3 subscribers

    Note over DS,DB: 3 reads → 1 DB query
